critical_positive: I think that we were both outgoing people, I dont imagine shy people would sign up for this.  We both talked a lot and asked each other questions.  I like that we were in different geographical locations.  We had a good conversation focused on where we live and did for a living.
critical_negative: I was a little disappointed to hear her discount the BLM movement, saying all lives matter or something to that effect.  I wonder how diverse the area is where she lives. She also looked down a lot and I could not see her face a good portion of the time.  We seemed to avoid talking too much politics, at least I know that I did since I was worried we might not have similar views.
